{"tid":1717054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大唔洗咁多人 想有貢獻唔該轉場","createTime":"2019-11-13T13:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:40:29.000Z","uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1695a9c8405fe1172c937385e4b0abea1a5063","tid":1717054,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"啲狗搞中大嘅意義係乜？<br />\n咪想打擊中大出去參與抗爭嘅人<br />\n佢地理撚得你炸左中大都唔會care<br />\n最著緊係出面抗爭點影響到經濟活動<br />\n<br />\n中大唔係唔洗守，但真係唔洗咁多人<br />\n琴日二橋個個逼住上前線<br />\n叫極企疏啲冇人聽<br />\n我本身做消防都越逼越後完全上唔前<br />\n仲有冇狗嘅地方都一大堆前線stand by<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句尤其係街外人真係唔洗咁多<br />\n地理環境唔熟悉<br />\n其他中大人仲要花多一倍心力<br />\n去安排你地衣食住行<br />\n出面家長又要冒風險係咁運物資<br />\n我多謝你地有心入嚟<br />\n但相信各位手足留喺自己區會更有意義<br />\n講緊係各區都打到開花<br />\n大量手足被捕<br />\n其他地區更需要你地<br />\n唔好浪費自己能力<br />\n<br />\n利申聽日就會番自己區"},{"pid":"4e38b20479e9fb6d51e9acd19c752cf040ec21c9","tid":1717054,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"morning sir, goodbye sir"},{"pid":"11c7e286311846351be754d15d03dc3ae5f04b4d","tid":1717054,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"又黎<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"fb6ea43a978817ad745fef4e3c4b0d1428e438b9","tid":1717054,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e38b20479e9fb6d51e9acd19c752cf040ec21c9","tid":1717054,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"morning sir, goodbye sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"理性討論？"},{"pid":"30c4fb59c67c7d530f0b0838ceba4d996fddd140","tid":1717054,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e38b20479e9fb6d51e9acd19c752cf040ec21c9","tid":1717054,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"morning sir, goodbye sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"97e007ee962b966a8936a651712ea95cd5266641","tid":1717054,"